replies.body:
Well Taric isn't completely useless
if he is against an all AD team he is pretty good and he is even better if his team also happens to be all AD (he has an armor shred and it scales with the armor he is likely to stack)

Taric's stun is pretty good at catching people out... however he isn't that great at peeling for his carry if more then 1 enemy dives his carry (well hopefully his heal and aura's will be enough to keep the carry alive)
